# {{.Name}}

A full-stack workflow application with React UI and Go backend, built with the [GoCodeAlone/workflow](https://github.com/GoCodeAlone/workflow) engine.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Go 1.22+
- Node.js 18+

### Development

Start the UI dev server:

```bash
cd ui
npm install
npm run dev
```

Start the backend (in a separate terminal):

```bash
go run . -config workflow.yaml
```

The backend runs on port 8080. The Vite dev server proxies API requests to it.

### Production Build

Build the UI:

```bash
cd ui
npm run build
```

Build and run the Go server (serves the built UI):

```bash
go build -o {{.Name}} .
./{{.Name}} -config workflow.yaml
```

Visit http://localhost:8080.

### API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | /health | Health check |
| GET | /api/items | List items |
| POST | /api/items | Create item |
| GET | /api/items/{id} | Get item |
| PUT | /api/items/{id} | Update item |
| DELETE | /api/items/{id} | Delete item |

